               <note type="summary" anchored="true">This document is a letter written by Andrew Jackson to Major William B. Lewis on December 14, 1807. In the letter, Jackson orders Major Lewis to allow the Tennessee Volunteers to return to Nashville, not enter them into service again soon, and pay them 10 dollars apiece for their weapons.</note>
