   <text>
      <body>
         <div subtype="1" type="letter">
            <pb n="1" facs="sl037a.small.jpg"/>
            <opener>
               <address>
                  <addrLine>
                     <name type="person">
                        <choice>
                           <abbr>Maj Wm</abbr>
                           <expan>Major William</expan>
                        </choice> B Lewis</name>
                  </addrLine>
                  <addrLine>Head Quarters</addrLine>
                  <addrLine>
                     <name type="person">H Strother</name> }</addrLine>
                  <addrLine>
                     <date when="1807-12-14">14th <choice>
                           <abbr>Dec.</abbr>
                           <expan>December</expan>
                        </choice> 1807</date>
                  </addrLine>
               </address>
               <salute>Sir</salute>
            </opener>
            <p>The Volunteers of <name type="place">Tennessee</name> having been permitted to return to <name type="place">Nashville</name> to await any order that may be given them by the <choice>
                  <abbr>Gov.</abbr>
                  <expan>Governor</expan>
               </choice> or the President; you will be good enough, if they should not be immediately ordered into service again to pay them for any complete stand of arms with its <unclear>aventrements</unclear> which they may deliver you, at the rate of ten dollars apiece.</p>
            <closer>
               <salute>I am respectfully</salute>
               <signed>
                  <emph>
                     <name type="person">Andrew Jackson</name>
                  </emph> Major <choice>
                     <abbr>Genl</abbr>
                     <expan>General</expan>
                  </choice>
               </signed>
               <address>
                  <addrLine>
                     <choice>
                        <abbr>Maj Wm</abbr>
                        <expan>Major William</expan>
                     </choice> B Lewis</addrLine>
                  <addrLine>at: <choice>
                        <abbr>Dep. Q.</abbr>
                        <expan>Department Quarter</expan>
                     </choice> Master }</addrLine>
               </address>
               <pb n="2" facs="sl037b.small.jpg"/>
               <address>
                  <addrLine>
                     <choice>
                        <abbr>Majr</abbr>
                        <expan>Major</expan>
                     </choice> William B Lewis</addrLine>
                  <addrLine>at: <choice>
                        <abbr>Dep. Q.</abbr>
                        <expan>Department Quarter</expan>
                     </choice> Master</addrLine>
                  <addrLine>
                     <name type="place">Nashville</name>
                  </addrLine>
               </address>
               <add>
                  <name type="person">
                     <choice>
                        <abbr>Genl</abbr>
                        <expan>General</expan>
                     </choice> Hall</name>
               </add>
            </closer>
         </div>
